metadata.name: The Melodic Minimalist
metadata.description:
**"The Melodic Minimalist"** - A synth legend who creates hauntingly beautiful melodies with sparse arrangements.

Each piece of concept art pays homage to the uncredited and often overlooked masterminds behind some of the biggest hits in the music world. From the producers in the shadows to the sound engineers behind the scenes, this collection shines a light on the unsung heroes of the music industry.

**Properties:**
Dimensions: 4608 × 3258 px
Editions: 1/1
Medium: AI
Year: 2023
